'''Characters''' in Yoshi's Cookie are based on the Super Mario Bros. universe.

== Playable Characters ==

=== Yoshi ===
The main protagonist in single-player modes.

'''Role:'''
* Controls the cookie puzzle field
* Appears on the left side of the screen
* Reacts to gameplay events

'''Animations:'''
* Happy expression when clearing cookies
* Worried expression when screen fills up
* Celebrates on level completion

=== Mario ===
Playable in multiplayer/VS modes.

'''Role:'''
* Player 1 character option
* Classic Mario sprite design
* Opponent to Yoshi in CPU battles

== Non-Playable Characters ==

=== Princess Peach ===
Appears in cutscenes and as decoration.

'''Appearances:'''
* Title screen
* Between-round animations
* Victory celebrations

=== Bowser ===
The antagonist who appears in certain modes.

'''Role:'''
* Final opponent in Action mode
* Harder AI difficulty
* Appears in ending sequences

